{"type":"log","step_name":"implement","message":"**Root cause:** `streamFullLog` in `handler.go` used `bufio.NewScanner` with the default 64KB buffer to read `full.log`. Claude Code's raw JSON output lines (especially \"assistant\" events containing tool_use blocks with file contents) regularly exceed 64KB. When the scanner hits a line that's too long, it silently stops reading — all subsequent log entries are lost.","timestamp":"2026-03-11T20:59:59.820525301Z"}
